posting_body: ['Views!', 'Views!', 'Views!', 'Spectacular  Panoramic City Skyline and Bay views, Stunningly remodeled 1BR with huge deck and parking!"', '$3695 per month !', '$250 per month for a carport parking', 'This home is a rare flat with no common walls to any neighbors, so is offers complete privacy and breathtaking views of the world re-known San Francisco Downtown City Skyline, South Bay, East Bay and North Bay.', 'With no stairs you park your car right outside in your private  carport and walk right into this spacious home with abundance of windows on all 4 sides rendering bright lights  and the drop dead gorgeous city, bay and forest sceneries on all 4 sides.', 'State of the art kitchen with Designer cabinetry is complimented with beautiful Quartz countertop and high end stainless steel appliances.', 'Our beautiful and brand new kitchen opens into an expansive living and dining area with a wood burning fire place', 'Completely remodeled bathroom with designer fixtures embellishing a tastefully selected and masterfully crafted tiles.', 'This is a true San Francisco Gem.', 'Neighborhood Amenities:', '• Within walking distance to Haight Street, Cole Valley, and Castro', '• Close to UCSF', '• Close to all public transportation', '• Great Walk To Twin Peaks', '• Whole Foods', '• Safeway', '• Amoeba Records', '• Bank of America', '• Wallgreens', 'Please call', 'show contact info', 'or e-mail us to schedule for a showing!------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------Rent:   $3695Bedroom: 1bathroom: 1Laundry:  w/d in the buildingparking: carportcat ok, dog ok,  no smokingStreet: Crown CourtCross Street: Raccoon DriveCity: San Francisco, CA 94114']
